{
  "message": "feat(conformance): add graph metrics conformance testing\n\nAdd conformance tests for graph metrics algorithms comparing Rust\nimplementation against Python NetworkX:\n- wiener_index - sum of all pairwise shortest path lengths\n- girth - length of shortest cycle (None for acyclic graphs)\n- degree_assortativity_coefficient - Pearson correlation of degrees\n- s_metric - sum of degree products over all edges\n- rich_club_coefficient - edge density among high-degree nodes\n\nAlso updates oracle contract to include metrics and traversal fixtures\nin the coverage manifest and J-CENTRALITY journey.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
